::Kaiser::
       Seeing the incoming shots he dives out of the way rolling back to his 
feet between Perceptor and the retreating Maximals.  This fortunate roll also 
allowed him to escape with only a minor cut to his wing from Devilcat's 
blade.  Wincing he fires another volley at both of his assailants, Perceptor 
and the invisible enemy known only by his blade. As an after thought he taps 
a button on his sheaths calling his scimitars back to their resting places.

--part1_f9.29bab954.2b805627_boundary
